Package: bayesglogit
Title: Bayesian Grouped Logistic Regression with Shrinkage Priors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tathastu", "Ghosh", email = "ghoshtathastu9@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements three grouped shrinkage priors for full Bayesian 
    logistic regression using Polya-Gamma data augmentation. The methods 
    include the Bayesian Grouped Horseshoe (BGHS), Grouped Regression with 
    Adaptive Shrinkage Priors (GRASP), and Group Inverse-Gamma Gamma (GIGG). 
    Full posterior inference is performed via Gibbs sampling with 
    Metropolis-Hastings within Gibbs for hyperparameters.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    MASS,
    BayesLogit,
    MCMCpack,
    GIGrvg,
    coda
